msgid ""
"Enable testing mode (t=y). DKIM signatures will be present but not enforced."
" Use during initial deployment."
msgstr "Modh tástála Cumasaigh (t=y). Beidh sínithe DKIM i láthair ach ní i bhfeidhm. Úsáid le linn imscaradh tosaigh."

