msgstr "Ní mór eochair phoiblí a bheith bailí sonraí bonn64-ionchódaithe"

#: lib/Module/DnsWizard/Service/DKIMWizard.php:216
msgid ""
"Public key seems unusually short. Ensure you copied the complete key from "
"your mail server."
msgstr "Dealraíonn eochair phoiblí neamhghnách gearr. A chinntiú go chóipeáil tú an eochair iomlán ó do fhreastalaí ríomhphoist."

#: lib/Module/DnsWizard/Service/DKIMWizard.php:221
msgid ""
"You pasted a PRIVATE KEY. Only the PUBLIC KEY should be in DNS. Never share "
"your private key!"
msgstr "Bhreathnaigh tú KEY PRIVATE. Níor chóir ach an KEY POIBLÍ a bheith i DNS. Ná roinnt do eochair phríobháideach!"

#: lib/Module/DnsWizard/Service/DKIMWizard.php:225
msgid ""
"Public key appears to contain PEM headers (BEGIN/END). Only the base64 "
"content between headers is needed."
msgstr "Dealraíonn eochair phoiblí go bhfuil headers PEM (BEGIN / END). Níl ach an t-ábhar base64 idir ceanntásca ag teastáil."

#: lib/Module/DnsWizard/Service/DKIMWizard.php:239
msgid ""
"Testing mode is enabled (t=y). DKIM signatures will not be enforced. Disable"
" this once testing is complete."
msgstr "Tá modh Tástáil ar chumas (t =y). Ní chuirfear sínithe DKIM i bhfeidhm. Díchumasaigh é seo nuair a thástáil críochnaithe."

