#: templates/default/list_views.html:15 templates/modern/list_views.html:15
msgid ""
"Views serve different zone variants to different clients based on the "
"network that queried the resolver. Each variant is named zone..variant (for "
"example, example.com..trusted) and must exist as a separate zone in PowerDNS"
" before it can be assigned here. Variants share a name but resolve "
"differently per view, so the same hostname can answer with different IPs "
"depending on the client's network."
msgstr "Freastalaíonn tuairimí leaganacha éagsúla crios le cliaint éagsúla bunaithe ar an líonra a rinne an réiteach. Tá gach leagan ainmnithe crios.variant (mar shampla, mar shampla.com.trusted) agus ní mór a bheith ann mar chrios ar leith i PowerDNS sular féidir é a shannadh anseo. Roinneann leabharlannaithe ainm ach réitíonn siad difriúil in aghaidh an dearcadh, mar sin is féidir leis an óstach céanna freagra a thabhairt le IPanna éagsúla ag brath ar líonra an chliaint."

